{"tid":886240,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"荷李活翻拍真人版《進擊的巨人》","createTime":"2018-11-02T03:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T13:56:18.000Z","uid":160969,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"71fad119c428cde60dec1ed17fac1e643ca6a455","tid":886240,"uid":160969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"由哈利波波嘅人去做監製，加埋Andres Muschietti應該唔會點差嘅 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本講談社日前發布消息稱，人氣漫畫《進擊的巨人》確定荷李活將翻拍真人版電影。電影宣布由《哈利波特》系列的David Heyman和《Heroes》男星岡政偉等共同擔任監製，並由《小丑回魂》的導演Andres Muschietti操刀執導。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2SEwgcH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SEwgcH&d=1VJWldnTnQw7AQGwQpx2r8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=88b7b668\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2SEwgcH</a>"},{"pid":"05ec5a89f4a74ca0b500a7a66368b5775a6232dc","tid":886240,"uid":33645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T08:19:52.000Z","msg":"想睇D唔著衫奇行種......"},{"pid":"2b9305a95b0d04d9fa1bad7f1a4920d165ba0fbe","tid":886240,"uid":60588,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T08:21:48.000Z","msg":"肯定好過日本自己拍個套先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e678758728d21e0d78ef7ac6becdd15b3e28dde","tid":886240,"uid":43839,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2b9305a95b0d04d9fa1bad7f1a4920d165ba0fbe","tid":886240,"uid":60588,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T08:21:48.000Z","msg":"肯定好過日本自己拍個套先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"鬥爛就有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日動跟本唔適合真人化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b28f69f6dfd4760920546adbff2bb0e15f0585b","tid":886240,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:20:31.000Z","msg":"兵長好難搵岩人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg